	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The first option.
<br />
<br />As you can imagine, 4 pairs of colors will not be enough to represent all the colors that "touch", so you'll need to use sprites to cover up a few glitches.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


